lts%20indicated%20that%20I%20burn%2C%20on%20average%2C%20about%201%2C400%20kcal%2Fday%20by%20just%20existing.%20(%3C%2Fspan%3EResearch%20suggests%3Cspan%3E%20this%20is%20in%20line%20with%20the%20average.)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20anyone%20looking%20to%20better%20understand%20how%20their%20body%20is%20changing%20over%20time%2C%20these%20tests%20can%20be%20a%20good%20starting%20point%2C%20but%20it%20doesn't%20tell%20you%20much%20in%20a%20vacuum.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e6240b08-78c9-4f48-9b66-72b1fc4dabc7%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20osteopath%20identified%20a%20source%20of%20back%20pain%20I'd%20never%20considered%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20last%20minute%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20meet%20with%20the%20clinic's%20osteopath%2C%20a%20licensed%20doctor%20whose%20medical%20practice%20looks%20at%20the%20whole%20person%20in%20a%20holistic%20sense.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20hadn't%20tried%20this%20area%20of%20medicine%20before.%20In%20New%20York%20City%2C%20one%20appointment%20with%20a%20DO%20(doctor%20of%20osteopathic%20medicine)%20could%20cost%20anywhere%20from%20%24135-%24400%20out%20of%20pocket%20for%20one%20appointment.%20Here%2C%20it%20cost%20me%20%E2%82%AC60%20(%2470).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELooking%20at%20me%2C%20she%20said%20she%20could%20tell%20I'd%20been%20doing%20calf%20raises%20on%20my%20right%20foot%20because%20that%20calf%20was%20notably%20bigger%20than%20my%20left.%20To%20achieve%20muscle%20balance%20between%20my%20left%20and%20right%20legs%2C%20she%20said%20I%20should%20be%20doing%20my%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-everyday-stretches-2017-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ephysical%20therapy%20exercises%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20my%20healthy%20leg%2C%20too%2C%20not%20just%20on%20the%20injured%20side.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThen%20she%20assessed%20my%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D