rk%20in%20August%202021%20and%20rented%20an%20apartment%20with%20one%20of%20my%20college%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e263da4c-6013-4990-8bfd-183913d8993a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20became%20a%20product%20marketing%20manager%20for%20ads%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20worked%20with%20the%20product%20manager%20to%20ensure%20that%20all%20of%20our%20products%20were%20ready%20to%20go%20to%20market.%20I%20learned%20a%20lot%2C%20and%20I%20learned%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20it%20were%20a%20launch%2C%20we'd%20recruit%20our%20target%20customers%20and%20do%20research%20with%20them%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20product%20was%20on%20the%20right%20track.%20If%20the%20products%20were%20already%20live%2C%20I'd%20work%20with%20customers%20to%20understand%20their%20pain%20points%20and%20find%20out%20how%20we%20could%20improve%20the%20existing%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20product%20I%20helped%20launch%20was%20Video%20Insights%2C%20which%20shared%20how%20much%20engagement%20you%20had%20at%20each%20point%20in%20your%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224ebdf441-c336-47b2-a4ac-d40e3fb776a0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20visited%20the%20office%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20October%202022%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20view%20of%20the%20New%20York%20skyline%20from%20the%20office%20was%20amazing.%20During%20the%20winter%20months%2C%20when%20the%20sun%20would%20set%20early%2C%20it%20was%20the%20ultimate%20place%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC2RJl0Dgro9%2F%3Figsh%3DMW5iMm85bWlhODd5ZQ%253D%253D%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewatch%20sunsets%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20walls%20were%20decorated%20with%20cool%20murals%20and%20neon%20artwork%20by%20local%20artists.%20The%20kitchen%20was%20filled%20with%20free%20snacks%20like%20Kit-Kats%2C%20Cup%20Noodles%2C%20and%20coffee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a1ab6f29-0b35-493a-9ece-40c42295943e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOver%20two%20years%2C%20the%20office%20cha