er%20own%20product%20to%20sell%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20fell%20into%20this%20e-commerce%20research%20hole%20%E2%80%94%20this%20whole%20world%20of%20being%20able%20to%20analyze%20supply%20and%20demand%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BEventually%2C%20I%20found%20a%20dog%20niche.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20decided%20to%20sell%20dog%20harnesses%2C%20found%20a%20manufacturer%20through%20Alibaba%2C%20and%20ordered%20about%20%245%2C000%20worth%20of%20inventory%20using%20her%20eBay%20earnings.%20The%20product%20arrived%20at%20her%20doorstep%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bit%20took%20me%20three%20hours%20to%20get%20them%20upstairs%20because%20it%20was%20carton%20after%20carton%20after%20carton%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHarrington%20listed%20and%20sold%20most%20of%20her%20initial%20inventory%20on%20eBay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20in%202012%2C%20when%20selling%20on%20Amazon%20was%20still%20uncharted%20territory.%20But%20when%20she%20discovered%20the%20relatively%20new%20platform%20and%20created%20a%20listing%2C%20%26quot%3Bthey%20sold%20out%20within%2024%20hours%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20I%20did%20the%20math%3A%20If%20I%20actually%20kept%20this%20in%20stock%2C%20how%20much%20would%20I%20do%20a%20year%20in%20revenue%3F%20And%20it%20was%20easily%20a%20million%20dollars.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20instant%20success%20on%20Amazon%20likely%20had%20more%20to%20do%20with%20timing%20than%20her%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%202013%2C%202014%2C%20there%20were%20not%20many%20options%20out%20there%2C%20so%20it%20was%20easy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BEvery%20year%20gets%20harder.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224c36f240-ec92-48b3-8bb5-6737108d0a1e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrom%20dog%20harnesses%20to%20cat%20doors%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20Harrington%20sold%20dog%20harnesses%20while%20working%20her%209-to-5.%20She%20ran%20a%20lean%20operation%20from%20her%20home%20in%20Arlington%2C%20Massachusetts%2C%20using%20the%20internet%20as%20a%20business%20coach%3A%20%26quot%3BGoogle%20was%20my%20best%20friend.%20I%20taught%20myself%20how%20to%20import%2C%20how%20to%20find%20a%20factory%2C%20how%20to%20wire%20payment%2C%20how%20to%20do%20marketing%2C%20how%20to%20find%20a%20bookkeeper%2C%20how%20to%20read%20a%20profit%20and%20loss%20statement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%202016%2C%20her%20e-commerce%20profit%20matched%20her%20salary%2C%20and%20she%20left%20the%20unsatisfying%20job%20that%20encouraged%20her%20to%20start%20a%20side%20project%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20gained%20an%20extra%20eight%20hours%20a%20day%2C%20she%20launched%20her%20second%20brand%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpurrfectportal.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPurrfect%20Portal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20to%20fill%20a%20gap%20in%20the%20pet%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22lisa%20harrington%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6880220285e81483682e7ef7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHarrington%20has%20designed%20and%20patented%20multiple%20interior%20cat%20doors.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Lisa%20Harrington%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20a%20cat%20lady%20%E2%80%94%20I've%20always%20been%20a%20cat%20lady%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20really%20wanted%20an%20interior%20cat%20door%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Harrington.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20went%20online%2C%20there%20was%20only%20one%20option.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20wasn't%20great%2C%20she%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20the%20quintessential%2C%20'I%20can%20do%20this%20better.'%20I%20know%20how%20to%20do%20this.%20I've%20found%20a%20factory%20in%20China.%20I've%20figured%20out%20how%20to%20bring%20cargo%20from%20one%20part%20of%20the%20world%20to%20another.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20designing%20a%20cat%20door%20would%20be%20a%20completely%20different%20and%20more%20complex%20project%20than%20producing%20dog%20harnesses.%20A%20mentor%20she%20found%20through%20the%20business%20program%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.score.org%2Ffind-mentor%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESCORE%3C%2Fa%3E%20connected%20her%20with%20engineers%20and%20a%20manufacturer%20who%20would%20help%20create%20the%20plastic%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20cat%20doors%20were%20profitable%20but%20not%20an%20immediate%20smash%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20the%20smaller%20of%20my%20two%20businesses%2C%20and%20it%20was%20just%20chugging%20along%20and%20growing%20year%20by%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Harrington%2C%20who%20started%20to%20notice%20a%20recurring%20customer%20comment%3A%20People%20were%20desperate%20for%20a%20closable%20door%2C%20rather%20than%20a%20cat%20door%20with%20flaps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20solution%20to%20her%20customer's%20woes%20was%20born%20out%20of%20a%20happy%20hour%20with%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSomeone%20said%2C%20'What%20about%20a%20miniature%20door%3F%20A%20little%20human%20door%20with%20a%20little%20doorknob%20and%20a%20little%20window%20and%20a%20little%20door%20knocker%2C'%26quot%3B%20recalled%20Harrington.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20everyone%20just%20lost%20their%20minds%2C%20even%20the%20non-cat%20people.%20And%20in%20my%20gut%2C%20I%20knew%20people%20would%20love%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20two%20years%20to%20bring%20the%20happy%20hour%20vision%20to%20life%2C%20but%20when%20it%20launched%20in%202020%2C%20%26quot%3Bpeople%20just%20lost%20their%20minds%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20catapulted%20to%20the%20top%20of%20the%20bestseller%20list%20pretty%20quickly.%20We%20were%20selling%20100%20units%20a%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202025%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe're%20the%20No.%201%20selling%20cat%20door%20on%20Amazon%2C%20and%20we%20have%20awesome%20patent%20protection%20on%20the%20invention%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20BI%20c