to%20manage%20everything.%20I'd%20rather%20get%20700%20to%201%2C000%20emails%20than%20sit%20in%20long%2C%20boring%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20do%20you%20prefer%20emails%20over%20meetings%2C%20Slack%2C%20texts%2C%20or%20other%20communication%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can%20easily%20search%20them%20decades%20later.%20I%20have%20emails%20going%20back%20to%20the%2090s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20your%20email%20habits%20help%20you%3F%20Do%20they%20make%20you%20more%20productive%3F%20Help%20you%20avoid%20distractions%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20asynchronous.%20I%20can%20write%20or%20respond%20any%20time%2C%20from%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world.%20That%20makes%20things%20much%20easier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20really%20no%20limit%20to%20the%20type%20or%20format%20of%20the%20content.%20I%20can%20include%20it%20in%20emails%20or%20attach%20whatever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEveryone%20has%20email.%20In%202025%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20anyone%20who%20doesn't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20fast.%20Particularly%20now%2C%20with%20Google's%20auto%20replies.%20For%20maybe%2010%20to%2020%25%20of%20my%20emails%2C%20I%20just%20have%20to%20choose%20one%20of%20Gmail's%20recommendations.%20If%20not%2C%20I%20can%20usually%20give%20very%20short%20responses.%20People%20expect%20them%20from%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20you%20keep%20your%20inbox%20organized%3F%20Do%20you%20use%20filters%2C%20folders%2C%20or%20an%20email%20extension%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20folders.%20I%20used%20to%20have%20too%20many%20emails%2C%20and%20Gmail%20couldn't%20keep%20up%2C%20so%20I%20had%20to%20segregate%20them%20into%20different%20accounts.%20Now%2C%20that%20typically%20isn't%20an%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spend%20most%20of%20my%20day%20trying%20to%20get%20my%20unreads%20under%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20acts%20as%20my%20tickler%20file%20and%20keeps%20what's%20important%20to%20me%2C%20right%20in%20front%20of%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHave%20you%20ever%20hired%20someone%20to%20help%20manage%20your%20email%3F%20If%20so%2C%20how%20did%20that%20go%3F%20If%20not%2C%20have%20you%20considered%20it%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENever.%20That%20just%20slows%20things%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHave%20you%20always%20preferred%20email%3F%20Or%20was%20there%20a%20moment%20in%20your%20career%20where%20you%20decided%20it%20was%20preferable%20to%20most%20other%20comms%20channels%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20sending%20messages%20in%20the%201980s%20on%20CompuServe.%20It%20was%20fast%20and%20easy.%20For%20my%20company%20back%20then%2C%20I%20had%20everyone%20get%20an%20address.%20It%20worked%20great%20then%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20still%20have%20a%20bunch%20of%20those%20folders%20with%20emails!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20you%20ever%20ignore%20your%20email%20(like%20on%20vacation)%3F%20Or%20do%20you%20always%20keep%20up%20with%20it%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20short%20period%20of%20time%2C%20sure.%20But%20for%20a%20full%20day%20or%20longer%2C%20only%20in%20extraordinary%20situations%20like%20a%20special%20event%20for%20a%20family%20member.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20a%20hard%20time%20disconnecting.%20It's%20faster%20to%20just%20get%20it%20out%20of%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20you%20like%20to%20achieve%20Inbox%20Zero%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWon't%20ever%20happen.%20I%20get%20down%20under%2010%20now%20and%20then%2C%20but%20I%20also%20use%20my%20unreads%20as%20a%20reminder%20of%20what%20I%20need%20to%20get%20done%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWould%20you%20ever%20consider%20letting%20AI%20write%20your%20emails%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnly%20the%20autoreply.%20Anything%20else%2C%20if%20I%20have%20a%20long%20response%2C%20I%20might%20use%20AI%20as%20a%20typing%20hack%20to%20save%20time%2C%20but%20I'm%20typically%20going%20to%20add%20some%20flavor%20somewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHave%20colleagues%2C%20b