an%20generate%20correct%20designs%20from%20experience%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20ton%20of%20people%20that%20would%20love%20to%20learn%2C%20but%20there's%20not%20enough%20manpower%20to%20actually%20teach%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Diode%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20Davide%20Asnaghi%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20raised%20%2411.4%20million%20in%20a%20Series%20A%20funding%20round%20led%20by%20Andreessen%20Horowitz%2C%20known%20as%20a16z%2C%20with%20participation%20from%20Caffeinated%20Capital%2C%20Box%20Group%2C%20and%20startup%20mentorship%20program%20Y%20Combinator.%20The%20round%20brings%20Diode's%20total%20funding%20to%20just%20over%20%2414%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDiode's%20cofounders%2C%20Davide%20Asnaghi%20and%20Lenny%20Khazan%2C%20were%20in%20the%20summer%202024%20Y%20Combinator%20cohort.%20There%2C%20they%20came%20up%20with%20the%20idea%20to%20help%20companies%20generate%20circuit%20board%20designs%20from%20scratch%20using%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20designing%20PCBs%20using%20pictures%20or%20diagrams%2C%20Diode%20translates%20PCB%20layouts%20into%20code%20using%20open-sourced%20AI%20software%20the%20company%20created.%20The%20startup%20says%20the%20software%20makes%20it%20easier%20to%20spot%20mistakes%20on%20the%20circuit%20boards%2C%20quickly%20reconfigure%20them%20for%20specific%20products%2C%20and%20scale%20production.%20Diode%20uses%20OpenAI%20and%20Anthropic%20large%20language%20models%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20using%20reinforcement%20learning%20to%20train%20smaller%20models%20to%20spot%20circuit%20board%20design%20mistakes%2C%20Asnaghi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDiode%20charges%20its%20customers%20for%20custom%20designing%20and%20manufacturing%20circuit%20boards.%20The%20startup%20outsources%20production%20to%20partners%20in%20California%20and%20on%20the%20East%20Coast%2C%20but%20Asnaghi's%20long-term%20goal%20is%20to%20become%20a%20%26quot%3Bone-stop%20shop%26quot%3B%20that%20will%20design%2C%20manufacture%2C%20and%20deliver%20PCBs%20to%20clients%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20eventual%20vision%20is%20that%20our%20customers%20should%20be%20able%20to%20push%20code%20to%20us%20in%20the%20same%20way%20that%20you%20deploy%20on%20AWS%2C%20and%20we%20will%20take%20that%20code%20and%20generate%20a%20physical%20product%20that%20gets%20shipped%20back%20to%20their%20assembler%20or%20their%20factory%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20is%20focused%20on%20working%20with%20robotics%2C%20medical%20device%2C%20and%20aerospace%20companies%20because%20%26quot%3Bthese%20three%20industries%20are%20very%20interested%20in%20manufacturing%20in%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20Asnaghi%20said.%20AI%20robotics%20startup%20Physical%20Intelligence%20and%20autonomous%20maritime%20startup%20Saronic%20are%20both%20Diode%20customers%2C%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDiode%20hopes%20to%20tap%20into%20Silicon%20Valley's%20renewed%20focus%20on%20scaling%20American%20manufacturing%2C%20particularly%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrumps-executive-orders-boost-vc-interest-in-defense-tech-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaerospace%20and%20defense%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Venture%20capitalists%20and%20founders%20building%20hard%20tech%20discussed%20this%20trend%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdefense-tech-china-american-manufacturing-reindustrialize-summit-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReindustrialize%20Summit%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20conference%20hosted%20in%20Detroit%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20terms%20of%20conflict%20and%20warfare%2C%20you%20need%20to%20be%20able%20to%20iterate%20on%20your%20hardware%20and%20electronic%20systems%20as%20quickly%20as%20you're%20iterating%20on%20your%20design%2C%26quot%3B%20Erin%20Price-Wright%2C%20a%20partner%20with%20A16z's%20American%20Dynamism%20practice%20%E2%80%94%20which%20invests%20in%20aerospace%2C%20defense%20tech%2C%20public%20safety%2C%20and%20other%20national%20security%20startups%20%E2%80%94%20told%20BI.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20designing%20one%20PCB%20board%20that's%20going%20to%20be%20in%20an%20airplane%20for%20the%2050-year%20lifetime%20of%20an%20airplane%2C%20you're%20thinking%20about%20having%20to%20redesign%20a%20new%20electronic%20stack%20every%20couple%20of%20months%20of%20a%20drone%20being%20deployed%20onto%20a%20battlefield.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20PCB%20design%20market%20is%20pretty%20crowded.%20Cadence%20Design%20Systems%20and%20Altium%20both%20make%20PCB%20design%20software.%20And%20Quilter%2C%20another%20startup%20that%20makes%20AI-powered%20PCB%20design%20software%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblog.quilter.ai%2Fseries-a%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraised%20a%20%2410%20million%20Series%20A%3C%2Fa%3E%20led%20by%20venture%20firm%20Benchmark%20in%20February%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20launching%20Diode%2C%20Asnaghi%20designed%20custom%20silicon%20chips%20at%20Chromatic%2C%20a%20stealth%20hard-tech%20startup.%20There%2C%20he%20experienced%20what%20he%20now%20sees%20as%20a%20recurring%20holdup%20in%20electrical%20engineering%3A%20PCB%20design%20errors%20that%20stalled%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20insane%20to%20me%20that%20you%20had%20this%20wonderful%20complex%20device%2C%20which%20is%20the%20custom%20silicon%2C%20and%20then%20the%20simpler%20node%20created%20unforeseen%20delays%20for%20no%20reason%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsnaghi%20also%20previously%20worked%20as%20an%20embedded%20software%20engineer%20at%20Apple%20and%20Butterfly%20Network%2C%20a%20medical%20imaging%20company.%20He%20earned%20his%20master's%20in%20engineering%20at%20Berkeley%20and%20studied%20engineering%20in%20college%20in%20Italy%20and%20at%20the%20Hong%20Kong%20University%20of%20Science%20and%20Technology%2C%20where%20he%20was%20an%20exchange%20student.%20His%20interest%20in%20electrical%20engineering%2C%20he%20told%20BI%2C%20stems%20from%20meeting%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20open%20source%20electronics%20platform%20Arduino.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BElectronics%20is%20the%20most%20magical%20of%20the%20engineering%20disciplines%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20take%20software%2C%20which%20is%20somewhat%20ethereal%2C%20and%20make%20it%20do%20things%20in%20the%20real%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsnaghi%20met%20Diode%20cofounder%20and%20chief%20technology%20officer%20Lenny%20Khazan%20at%20Butterfly%20Network%2C%20where%20Khazan%20was%20an%20intern.%20He%20previously%20worked%20as%20a%20software%20engineer%20at%20Chromatic%20and%20Instabase%2C%20an%20AI%20data%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20seeing%20a%20rise%20in%20the%20importance%20of%20physical%20products%2C%26quot%3B%20Asnaghi%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20more%20need%20for%20infrastructure%20%E2%80%94%20data%20centers%2C%20power%20generation%2C%20all%20of%20these%20things%20rely%20on%20prepared%20circuit%20boards%20on%20some%20level.%20Virtually%20any%20product%20that%20has%20some%20electronics%20in%20it%20will%20have%20a%20circuit%20board.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-circuit-board-diode-a16z-series-a-y-combinator-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753261202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687ffb8485e81483682e7d57%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-circuit-board-diode-a16z-series-a-y-combinator-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Andreessen%20Horowitz%20leads%20a%20Series%20A%20investment%20in%20Diode%20Computers%2C%20which%20translates%20printed%20circuit%20board%20layouts%20into%20code.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jhornstein%40insider.com%20(Julia%20Hornstein)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-circuit-board-diode-a16z-series-a-y-combinator-202