0prosecutors%20say%20in%20court%20papers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20details%20may%20be%20discussed%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20when%20the%20two%20accused%20kidnappers%2C%20cryptocurrency%20investors%20William%20Duplessie%2C%2037%2C%20of%20Miami%2C%20and%20John%20Woeltz%2C%2037%2C%20of%20Kentucky%2C%20will%20ask%20a%20judge%20to%20free%20them%20on%20%241%20million%20bail%20each%20with%20separate%20home%20confinement%20in%20the%20homes%20of%20their%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20their%20last%20court%20appearance%2C%20in%20June%2C%20the%20defendants'%20lawyers%20told%20New%20York%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluigi-mangiones-judge-new-york-murder-gregory-carro-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJustice%20Gregory%20Carro%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20kidnapping-torture%20allegations%20are%20completely%20fabricated.%20(Carro%20is%20the%20same%20judge%20assigned%20to%20the%20state-level%20murder%20case%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faetna-mistakenly-revealed-luigi-mangione-medical-records-defense-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELuigi%20Mangione%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20accused%20in%20the%20December%202024%20assassination%20of%20UnitedHealthcare%20CEO%20Brian%20Thompson.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20crypto-kidnapping%20victim%2C%20Michael%20Carturan%2C%2028%2C%20was%20a%20business%20partner%20and%20friend%20to%20Duplessie%20and%20Woeltz%2C%20the%20lawyers%20said.%20They%20said%20Carturan%20was%20at%20the%20townhouse%20willingly%2C%20for%20what%20they%20described%20as%20a%2017-day%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20videos%20of%20Carturan%20%26quot%3Bsmoking%20crack%2C%20having%20the%20time%20of%20his%20life%2C%20being%20involved%20in%20a%20sex%20orgy%2C%20being%20dragged%20around%20by%20a%20woman%20while%20he's%20naked%20inside%20the%20location%26quot%3B%20while%20wearing%20a%20BDSM%20collar%2C%20defense%20lawyer%20Sanford%20Talkin%20told%20the%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETalkin%20told%20the%20jud