3ac108%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHis%20next%20role%20might%20not%20be%20in%20management%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20a%20layoff%20is%20rarely%20happy%20news%2C%20Melekian%20said%20the%20timing%20was%20relatively%20fortunate%3A%20He%20had%20already%20been%20planning%20to%20move%20back%20to%20France%20for%20personal%20and%20family%20reasons.%20With%20his%20parents%20getting%20older%2C%20he%20wanted%20to%20be%20closer%20in%20case%20they%20needed%20support.%20His%20youngest%20son%20also%20just%20graduated%20from%20high%20school%20and%20plans%20to%20attend%20school%20in%20France%20this%20fall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20our%20children%20and%20our%20own%20aging%20parents%20all%20being%20in%20France%2C%20there%20was%20nothing%20holding%20my%20wife%20and%20me%20back%20in%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMelekian%20said%20he's%20already%20sold%20his%20home%20in%20the%20US%20and%20returned%20to%20France%2C%20but%20hasn't%20started%20actively%20job%20hunting%20yet.%20He%20plans%20to%20do%20so%20later%20this%20summer%20once%20he's%20more%20settled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20his%20job%20search%20picks%20up%2C%20he's%20not%20sure%20whether%20he'll%20prioritize%20management%20roles%20or%20individual%20contributor%20positions.%20He%20said%20he%20may%20prefer%20a%20role%20with%20less%20managerial%20responsibility%20%E2%80%94%20one%20where%20he%20can%20have%20a%20more%20direct%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BManager%20roles%20certainly%20align%20with%20my%20experience%2C%20but%20I%20may%20also%20consider%20roles%20where%20I%20can%20contribute%20directly%20with%20my%20expertise%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMelekian%20said%20he%20has%20a%20few%20pieces%20of%20advice%20for%20people%20who%20are%20dealing%20with%20layoffs%20or%20career%20transitions.%20First%2C%20rely%20on%20others%20for%20advice%20and%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou'd%20be%20surprised%20how%20willing%20people%20are%20to%20share%20their%20own%20similar%20experiences%2